An additional attraction is a small drone flown by a robotics startup above its booth for attention. Event staff scan registrations and hand out lanyards at the entrance, while recruiters distribute tote bags filled with branded notebooks and pens. Students clutch resumes inside branded folders, and an alumni panel discusses how to prepare for technical interviews.

Human resources teams take notes on tablets as students network and introduce themselves. Career counselors advise attendees to maintain eye contact and guide unsure students toward relevant industries. Small groups analyze which recruiters appeared most enthusiastic, and a robotics startup attracts attention to its booth by flying a small drone above it. Announcement chimes signal the final hour of the fair.
